{"id":"api/core/provideZoneChangeDetection","title":"provideZoneChangeDetection","contents":"<article>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb-container\">\n    <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n      <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n        {\n          \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n          \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n          \"itemListElement\": [\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/core\", \"name\": \"@angular/core\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/core/provideZoneChangeDetection\", \"name\": \"provideZoneChangeDetection\" } }\n          ]\n        }\n      </script>\n        <a href=\"/api\">API</a> &gt; <a href=\"api/core\">@angular/core</a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/17.3.0-next.1/packages/core/src/change_detection/scheduling/ng_zone_scheduling.ts#L91-L120\" aria-label=\"查看源码\" title=\"查看源码\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  </div>\n  <header class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"providezonechangedetection\">provideZoneChangeDetection<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/provideZoneChangeDetection#providezonechangedetection\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label function\">function</label>\n  </header>\n  \n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n  <section class=\"short-description\">\n    <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"ad3qj268kz3sxj0fuzsjmd5mz\">为使用 <code><a href=\"api/platform-browser/bootstrapApplication\" class=\"code-anchor\">bootstrapApplication</a></code> 引导的应用程序提供基于 <code><a href=\"api/core/NgZone\" class=\"code-anchor\">NgZone</a></code> 的变更检测。</p>\n\n    <p><a href=\"api/core/provideZoneChangeDetection#description\">查看更多...</a></p>\n  </section>\n\n  <div class=\"overload-info\">\n  <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\"> <span class=\"member-name\"><a href=\"api/core/provideZoneChangeDetection\" class=\"code-anchor\">provideZoneChangeDetection</a></span>(options?: <a href=\"api/core/NgZoneOptions\" class=\"code-anchor\">NgZoneOptions</a>): <a href=\"api/core/EnvironmentProviders\" class=\"code-anchor\">EnvironmentProviders</a></code-example>\n\n  <h6 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"parameters\">参数</h6>\n  <table class=\"is-full-width list-table parameters-table function-overload-parameters\">\n  <tbody>\n    <tr class=\"function-overload-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"bctpqv6pe3qufag0kdnkhac2q\"><a id=\"\"></a>\n        <code>options</code></td>\n      <td class=\"param-type\"><code><a href=\"api/core/NgZoneOptions\" class=\"code-anchor\">NgZoneOptions</a></code></td>\n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n        <p>可选值。默认值为 <code>undefined</code>。</p>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n  <h6 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"returns\">返回值</h6>\n  <p><code><a href=\"api/core/EnvironmentProviders\" class=\"code-anchor\">EnvironmentProviders</a></code></p>\n\n</div>\n\n\n<section class=\"see-also\">\n  <h2 id=\"see-also\">参见<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/provideZoneChangeDetection#see-also\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <ul>\n    <li><a href=\"api/platform-browser/bootstrapApplication\"><code>bootstrapApplication</code></a></li>\n    <li><a href=\"api/core/NgZoneOptions\"><code>NgZoneOptions</code></a></li>\n  </ul>\n</section>\n\n<section class=\"description\">\n  <h2 id=\"description\">说明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/provideZoneChangeDetection#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"a1exokqf8sxaz1e9j7w0x1fen\">默认情况下，应用程序中已经提供了 <code><a href=\"api/core/NgZone\" class=\"code-anchor\">NgZone</a></code>。该提供程序允许你在 <code><a href=\"api/core/NgZone\" class=\"code-anchor\">NgZone</a></code> 中配置诸如 <code>eventCoalescing</code> 之类的选项。此提供程序不适用于 <code><a href=\"api/platform-browser/platformBrowser\" class=\"code-anchor\">platformBrowser</a>().bootstrapModule</code>，它使用 <code><a href=\"api/core/BootstrapOptions\" class=\"code-anchor\">BootstrapOptions</a></code> 代替。</p>\n  <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"72g6w0fdod396m2kih9efyoog\">进一步的信息可在\n<a href=\"api/core/provideZoneChangeDetection#usage-notes\">使用说明...</a>中找到。</p>\n</section>\n\n\n<section class=\"usage-notes\">\n  <h2 id=\"usage-notes\">使用说明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/provideZoneChangeDetection#usage-notes\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <code-example language=\"typescript\">\n<a href=\"api/platform-browser/bootstrapApplication\" class=\"code-anchor\">bootstrapApplication</a>(MyApp, {providers: [\n  <a href=\"api/core/provideZoneChangeDetection\" class=\"code-anchor\">provideZoneChangeDetection</a>({eventCoalescing: true}),\n]});\n</code-example>\n\n</section></div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/core\n - api/core/NgZoneOptions\n - api/platform-browser/testing/BrowserTestingModule\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/core\n - api/core/BootstrapOptions\n - api/core/EnvironmentProviders\n - api/core/NgZone\n - api/core/NgZoneOptions\n - api/core/provideZoneChangeDetection#description\n - api/core/provideZoneChangeDetection#providezonechangedetection\n - api/core/provideZoneChangeDetection#see-also\n - api/core/provideZoneChangeDetection#usage-notes\n - api/platform-browser/bootstrapApplication\n - api/platform-browser/platformBrowser\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/17.3.0-next.1/packages/core/src/change_detection/scheduling/ng_zone_scheduling.ts#L91-L120\n-->"}